data.description: Here is your chance to own a 3 bedroom home plus 4th nonconforming room in the heart of  historic Plattsmouth. Enjoy original hardwood floors in the spacious living room with the opportunity to remove the flooring throughout the main to discover the hardwood beneath. The kitchen is extra large with plenty of countertop and storage, plus enjoy the brand new subway tile backsplash! There is a 3/4 bathroom on the main floor plus a full bathroom in the basement! The laundry area offers a nice storage area as a bonus to the home. The backyard is fully fenced and very spacious to allow room for people and pups alike to play. Located close to main roads, shopping, parks and other amenities. Welcome home!! Please note property is being sold as is, where-is with no repairs or warranties to be made by the sellers.
